Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chris's favorite venues
des: I love to travel, and I love live music. So I'm creating this skill to share my favorite music venues around the country. You can share your location to get the closest one to you, and I'll update with extra special events I'm excited about. See you at the next show!
